commitResults.messageTitle: Level-2, added list class for storing and showing list of activity. changed echoing input to adding input into the list and a list cmd to show the content of the list.
Level-2, changed login function from if-else statements into switch statement and partially implemented level-3 checkboxes
Level-4, Added todo, event, deadline. replaced task in duke with todo. Added checks for done out of range. Added toString for task for better inheritance. Added different add tasks behavior to list
A-TextUiTesting, added content to input.txt, changed EXPECTED.TXT to comply with input.txt.
Level-5. Handled invalid input (eg todo    , event     ) and done with no number
Level-6. Implemented delete task function as well as custom message when there is no take in the list
Level-5A-Exceptions. Added DukeException.java as an umbrella exception to signify an unknown prompt
Added extractInt function to Duke to make code neater, also added documentations and removed tostring() from addtodo/deadline/event
Level-7 Add save function by implementing serializable interface for Task and add writeToFile and loadFromFile function in List
Level-8, add LocalDate to Deadline but currently only accepts dd/mm/yyyy or dd-mm-yyyy as date format, also Deadline constructor now throws DukeException
A-MoreOOP: add Parser, Storage, Ui for more OOP
A-Packages: organize the files into packages util,task,exception
A-JUnit, add DeadlineTest.java and ToDoTest.java for basic testing, updated exception handling in Deadline and List
A-JavaDoc, add Javadocs to most methods and classes
A-CodingStandard, ensure code conforms to coding standard
Level-9, add find case to Parser.java as well as find method to List.java and getDescription method to Tasks to support find method
